 is\nbecoming visible. These deeply embedded stars may be evolving off of the AGB\nand/or they may have non-spherical dust geometries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2016 20:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-27"}
