eir discrete spectra only containing real\nand discrete numbers $\\tau_m$ for $m=0,\\pm1,\\pm2,...$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Apr 2016 09:29:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2016 09:25:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2016 14:55:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-18"}
